                            <comment id="17455090" author="davsclaus" created="Wed, 8 Dec 2021 09:50:17 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;That is because you use toD and &quot;abuse&quot; the Exchange.HTTP_URI header.&lt;br/&gt;
You can use to then it should work&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17455229" author="marat.gubaidullin@gmail.com" created="Wed, 8 Dec 2021 13:03:45 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;1. &lt;b&gt;to&lt;/b&gt; works for camel-vertx-http&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
.to(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;vertx-http:${header.CamelHttpUri}&quot;&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;2. However &lt;b&gt;toD&lt;/b&gt; works for camel-http&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
.toD(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;${header.CamelHttpUri}&quot;&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;3. But &lt;b&gt;to&lt;/b&gt; &lt;font color=&quot;red&quot;&gt;does not work&lt;/font&gt; for camel-http&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
.to(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;${header.CamelHttpUri}&quot;&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This is kind of confusing&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17456270" author="davsclaus" created="Thu, 9 Dec 2021 09:37:02 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Ad 2)&lt;br/&gt;
This only works because the http uri is with https that is the http component name also (http/https)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;So if you do it as&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
.toD(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;http:${header.CamelHttpUri}&quot;&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Then it fails just like vertx-http does&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17456338" author="davsclaus" created="Thu, 9 Dec 2021 10:51:30 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;There was a bug in toD when using vertx-http when compared to camel-http.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
